1. 进入「离线开发-数据开发-周期任务」页面
2. 创建数据同步任务Hive2OBOracle, 配置如下:数据来源: Hive 3.x(CDP), employees_hive选择目标: OceanBase 4.3.x(Oracle), 一键建表employees_hive字段映射: 同名映射其它选项保持默认后, 保存并提交
3. 临时运行, 查看结果

4. 执行SQL查询OBOracle表数据: 
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
TRUNCATE TABLE employees_hive;
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
5. 周期运行, 查看结果
6. 执行SQL查询OBOracle表数据: 
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
TRUNCATE TABLE employees_hive;
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
7. 补数据运行, 查看结果
8. 执行SQL查询OBOracle表数据: 
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
TRUNCATE TABLE employees_hive;
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
9. 进入「离线开发-数据开发-手动任务」页面
10. 创建数据同步任务Hive2OBOracle后, 保存并提交
11. 临时运行, 查看结果

12. 执行SQL查询OBOracle表数据: 
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
TRUNCATE TABLE employees_hive;
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
13. 手动运行, 查看结果

14. 执行SQL查询OBOracle表数据: 
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;
TRUNCATE TABLE employees_hive;
SELECT * FROM employees_hive;

1. 进入「离线开发-数据开发-周期任务」页面
2. 创建数据同步任务OBOracle2Hive, 配置如下:
数据来源: OceanBase 4.3.x(Oracle), PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD
选择目标: Hive 3.x(CDP), 一键建表PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD
字段映射: 同名映射
其它选项保持默认后, 保存并提交
3. 临时运行, 查看结果

4. 执行SQL查询Hive表数据: 
SELECT * FROM PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
TRUNCATE TABLE PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
SELECT * FROM PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
5. 周期运行, 查看结果
6. 执行SQL查询Hive表数据: 
SELECT * FROM PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
TRUNCATE TABLE PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
SELECT * FROM PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
7. 补数据运行, 查看结果
8. 执行SQL查询Hive表数据: 
SELECT * FROM PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
TRUNCATE TABLE PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
SELECT * FROM PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
9. 进入「离线开发-数据开发-手动任务」页面
10. 创建数据同步任务OBOracle2Hive后, 保存并提交到运维中心手动运行
11. 执行SQL查询Hive表数据: 
SELECT * FROM PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
TRUNCATE TABLE PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;
SELECT * FROM PORT_VESSEL_OPERATION_RECORD;

